===Adjective===
'''frigid'''

# Very [[cold]]; lacking [[warmth]]; [[icy]].
# Chilly in [[manner]]; lacking [[affection]] or [[zeal]]; [[impassive]].
# Sexually [[unresponsive]], especially of a woman.

